    <description><![CDATA[
      <p>Yonyou U8Cloud, NC5 NC6 NCCloud YonBip and other series of software development tools</p>
        <p>English: </p>
        If you do not need to edit metadata and new document development can directly create idea ordinary projects.
        You can change the name of the old project folder and create a new folder with the same path, and then copy the files in the folder.
        <ul>
            <li>First time opening project - Required steps:</li>
                <li>1. Tools -> Configure NC HOME.</li>
                <li>2. Tools -> update NC library dependencies execute dependency update!</li>
                <li>3. Tools -> generate default NC run configuration!</li>
                <li>4. After you perform the preceding steps for the first time, the project will generate the default client public Private test several source folders. Manually modify the IDEA attribute of several folders in the project structure to correct values</li>
                <li>5. Select Use Module path to set the output path of test class and non-test class respectively.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Chinese: </p>
      如果不需要元数据编辑和新单据开发的 可以直接新建idea普通的项目就行。如果需要的 可以用eclipse新建好项目和组件以后，用idea打开项目，<br>
      因为idea有时候有bug打不开eclipse项目 可以老项目文件夹改革个名称 然后idea新建一个同路径的，然后吧文件夹文件复制进来(机智不)。 <br>
           <ul>
              <li>第一次打开项目-必须步骤：</li>
                <li>1. Tools -> 配置NC HOME   进行NC HOME配置！</li>
                <li>2. Tools -> 更新NC 库依赖 执行依赖更新!</li>
                <li>3. Tools -> 生成默认NC运行配置!(如果重启IDEA后丢失了运行配置 可以再次执行这个)</li>
                <li>4. 第一次执行上面步骤以后，会生成项目默认的client public private test 几个源文件夹 请手工在 项目结构修改几个文件夹的IDEA属性为正确值</li>
                <li>5. 请注意 模块的编译输出路径要选 use module path 分别设置test和非test class输出路径。</li>
         </ul>

    ]]></description>

